    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed the required credibility level. Test conditions factor achieved level 1 against a required level 2; this shortfall is accepted given the standardized and widely validated nature of the ASTM F1717 protocol and the availability of N=11 experimental replicates across two laboratories. Overall model credibility is sufficient to support regulatory submission for the non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw design.",
